To install FLUX, open either the Linux or Mac installation instructions and follow them closely. Windows is not supported. 
These instructions will install the python wrapper FLUXpype, located in [this repository](https://github.com/GillySpace27/fluxpype). 
FLUXpype enables easier installation as well as orchistration of many of the FLUX core functions. 

Documentation of the FLUX core relaxer is now to be found at
https://github.com/d-lamb/fluxon-mhd/wiki ; it may be collated into
here for a future release.  The original design docs are kept in "old"
for historical reasons.

-CED 31-Oct-2007
